    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's ready for its next adventure! This car has been well-cared for and is in really solid shape, making it a perfect pick if you want something dependable and fun to drive. It runs like a dream and is super clean inside and out. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a test drive\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 power plant, paired with a tactile G96 six-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear architecture that provides exceptional lateral grip. Mechanically sound, the engine benefits from VarioCam Plus variable valve timing and a documented IMS bearing retrofit, ensuring the integrity of the intermediate shaft. The braking system retains its factory-spec ventilated rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers, offering consistent thermal management and firm pedal modulation. A well-sorted driver's car that balances analog engagement with mechanical reliability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior with minor wear. Regular maintenance performed. Solid body, no major accidents.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
