    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic paint that still holds a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection will reveal the minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has remained a strictly smoke-free environment. The leather upholstery is soft and intact, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; I have kept a meticulous log of all services, including recent fluid flushes and a new set of brake pads. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need an immediate trip to the shop. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers the peace of mind that comes from a vehicle that has been consistently garaged and serviced on schedule.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
